document.full_text: japanese workers entered the no.1 reactor building at the crippled fukushima daiichi nuclear plant thursday for the first time since a hydrogen explosion ripped off its roof a day after a devastating march 11 earthquake and tsunami.
document.title: workers enter japan reactor for first time since blast
